1
00:01:28,362 --> 00:01:33,416
[Adapted from Che Ye Liu Xiang's
novel of the same name]

2
00:01:33,416 --> 00:01:38,091
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:44,958 --> 00:01:46,581
Hurry up and get ready to go, Mr. Bei.

4
00:01:46,581 --> 00:01:49,416
Do I have to come up and get you myself?

5
00:01:49,416 --> 00:01:50,875
Big Bro.

6
00:01:50,875 --> 00:01:53,497
The soup will be ready in half an hour.

7
00:02:07,375 --> 00:02:08,951
What a pity.

8
00:02:11,833 --> 00:02:14,091
I'm afraid...

9
00:02:15,416 --> 00:02:17,633
I won't be able to have soup tonight.

10
00:02:26,791 --> 00:02:29,591
Big Bro, there's someone outside.

11
00:02:40,332 --> 00:02:41,875
No way, Mr. Bei.

12
00:02:41,875 --> 00:02:43,041
It doesn't look like
you're just fooling around with him.

13
00:02:43,041 --> 00:02:44,978
Mind your own business.

14
00:02:46,207 --> 00:02:47,875
All right.

15
00:02:47,875 --> 00:02:49,375
Anyway, it's better this way.

16
00:02:49,375 --> 00:02:50,919
It's safe.

17
00:02:58,833 --> 00:02:59,833
Lv Qing.

18
00:02:59,833 --> 00:03:02,040
You're really a master at picking places.

19
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,125
In a place like this,

20
00:03:03,125 --> 00:03:05,883
even mosquitoes would need
a credit check to get in.

21
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,374
Finally got rid of that tag along?

22
00:03:17,374 --> 00:03:19,000
Oh, my dear young master.

23
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,977
Let's talk business first.

24
00:03:22,082 --> 00:03:23,458
Xiao Fan.

25
00:03:23,458 --> 00:03:25,291
Bring the documents over.

26
00:03:25,291 --> 00:03:26,833
Yes, they're on the table.

27
00:03:26,833 --> 00:03:28,956
The driver is waiting for you downstairs.

28
00:03:31,141 --> 00:03:36,215
[Document Folder]

29
00:03:41,541 --> 00:03:43,375
Now this is something new.

30
00:03:43,375 --> 00:03:46,291
So, I think...

31
00:03:46,291 --> 00:03:47,874
Oh, Xiao Fan is here.

32
00:03:47,874 --> 00:03:50,458
We've been waiting for you.

33
00:03:50,458 --> 00:03:52,206
Have a seat.

34
00:03:52,206 --> 00:03:53,291
Goodness.

35
00:03:53,291 --> 00:03:54,958
I knew it.

36
00:03:54,958 --> 00:03:57,198
Big Bro, your documents.

37
00:03:58,499 --> 00:04:01,529
I... I also brought some soup.

38
00:04:05,666 --> 00:04:07,458
Go and share it with everyone outside.

39
00:04:07,458 --> 00:04:09,008
Okay.

40
00:04:14,916 --> 00:04:17,583
Lv Qing, you just leave
documents like that at home?

41
00:04:17,583 --> 00:04:19,517
Are you sure he won't peek?

42
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,833
That's the good thing about Xiao Fan.

43
00:04:27,833 --> 00:04:29,541
He's timid and cautious.

44
00:04:29,541 --> 00:04:32,750
He might not be the sharpest,
but he knows his place.

45
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:33,791
Oh, please.

46
00:04:33,791 --> 00:04:35,291
He doesn't know a damn thing.

47
00:04:35,291 --> 00:04:36,375
Even if you laid it out for him,

48
00:04:36,375 --> 00:04:38,032
would he even understand it?

49
00:04:44,954 --> 00:04:46,442
Big Bro.

50
00:04:53,833 --> 00:04:55,474
Zi Yang.

51
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:17,458
Look, this guy doesn't even
have a brokerage account.

52
00:05:17,458 --> 00:05:19,959
Why the hell is he reading
the securities newspaper all day?

53
00:05:21,041 --> 00:05:23,958
I'm just browsing.

54
00:05:23,958 --> 00:05:25,833
Look at what you're saying.

55
00:05:25,833 --> 00:05:27,999
Ordinary people like to read Global Times, too.

56
00:05:27,999 --> 00:05:31,791
So what? Are they all UN Secretary-Generals?

57
00:05:31,791 --> 00:05:34,375
I think Lv Qing is right.

58
00:05:34,375 --> 00:05:38,041
Xiao Fan isn't cut out
for speculation or stocks.

59
00:05:38,041 --> 00:05:41,041
The best thing about Xiao Fan
is his simplicity.

60
00:05:41,041 --> 00:05:42,625
Simplicity?

61
00:05:42,625 --> 00:05:44,522
More like stupid and ordinary.

62
00:05:45,625 --> 00:05:46,708
Zhuo Xin.

63
00:05:46,708 --> 00:05:48,477
Are you out of your mind?

64
00:05:50,291 --> 00:05:53,000
Why else would you be acting so cocky?

65
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,958
Look at you. You just had to
make Lv Qing speak up.

66
00:05:54,958 --> 00:05:57,791
How was it? Quite a mouthful, wasn't it?

67
00:05:57,791 --> 00:05:59,857
Come on. Let's have a drink.

68
00:06:00,791 --> 00:06:02,125
I saw that report Lv Qing had.

69
00:06:02,125 --> 00:06:05,832
The news about loosening
stock market regulations is true.

70
00:06:05,832 --> 00:06:06,833
Think about it.

71
00:06:06,833 --> 00:06:09,707
The Songnan and Yunjing gangs
are fighting so hard.

72
00:06:09,707 --> 00:06:11,583
To boost the economy,

73
00:06:11,583 --> 00:06:14,500
they have to let the Songnan gang take over.

74
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:16,294
The price of rice is going to rise.

75
00:06:17,125 --> 00:06:19,125
It's going to skyrocket.

76
00:06:19,125 --> 00:06:22,583
It's expected to hit one yuan within two years.

77
00:06:22,583 --> 00:06:25,750
Rice is only fifty cents a pound now.

78
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:27,625
The government is subsidizing it now

79
00:06:27,625 --> 00:06:29,750
to keep the price of rice stable.

80
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:31,083
But they can't hold it much longer.

81
00:06:31,083 --> 00:06:33,041
The situation in the south is unstable.

82
00:06:33,041 --> 00:06:34,750
And there's a red-headed document

83
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:36,750
ordering an increase in rice reserves.

84
00:06:36,750 --> 00:06:39,803
So, the price of rice is bound to go up.

85
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:45,833
If rice goes up,
wheat will likely follow suit.

86
00:06:45,833 --> 00:06:48,291
That's why, by the time
we pull out of the stock market,

87
00:06:48,291 --> 00:06:49,625
we'll be just in time to catch

88
00:06:49,625 --> 00:06:51,923
this wave of rising prices
in agricultural products.

89
00:06:53,916 --> 00:06:56,833
Let's just get out of the stock market first.

90
00:07:06,458 --> 00:07:07,958
<i>Why are you calling so late?</i>

91
00:07:07,958 --> 00:07:09,250
Mom.

92
00:07:09,250 --> 00:07:11,666
Did we plant any wheat this year?

93
00:07:11,666 --> 00:07:12,666
<i>You silly child.</i>

94
00:07:12,666 --> 00:07:13,750
<i>Calling in the middle of the night</i>

95
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:15,500
<i>just to ask if we planted wheat?</i>

96
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,999
<i>Why would we plant wheat?</i>

97
00:07:16,999 --> 00:07:19,333
<i>If we plant wheat now,
we'd lose dozens of yuan per mu.</i>

98
00:07:19,333 --> 00:07:20,500
<i>Who would still plant wheat?</i>

99
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:22,541
<i>No one in the village plants it anymore.</i>

100
00:07:22,541 --> 00:07:23,958
Not even enough for us to eat?

101
00:07:23,958 --> 00:07:26,000
<i>We did when you were still at home.</i>

102
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,375
<i>But your dad's picky now.</i>

103
00:07:27,375 --> 00:07:28,625
<i>He loves that wheat from Huanglong.</i>

104
00:07:28,625 --> 00:07:30,375
<i>So, we just dug up all our own wheat.</i>

105
00:07:30,375 --> 00:07:31,750
- Mom!
<i>- We're planting apple trees this year.</i>

106
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:34,916
But why aren't you
planting food for yourselves?

107
00:07:34,916 --> 00:07:37,875
If you can't buy wheat later,
won't that be a problem?

108
00:07:37,875 --> 00:07:39,541
<i>How could we not be able to buy it?</i>

109
00:07:39,541 --> 00:07:41,000
<i>They sell it right here in the village.</i>

110
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,250
<i>We don't even have to go to the county seat.</i>

111
00:07:42,250 --> 00:07:44,916
We eat 400 to 500 catties of wheat a year.

112
00:07:44,916 --> 00:07:47,458
If it goes up to one yuan a catty next year,

113
00:07:47,458 --> 00:07:49,625
won't you have worked all year for nothing?

114
00:07:49,625 --> 00:07:50,875
<i>One yuan a catty?</i>

115
00:07:50,875 --> 00:07:52,750
<i>Xiao Fan, are you serious?</i>

116
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:55,040
<i>Huh? Did you hear some inside news?</i>

117
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,458
<i>People will starve at that price!</i>

118
00:07:56,458 --> 00:07:59,289
<i>Oh dear! Xiao Fan said
the price of wheat is going to skyrocket!</i>

119
00:07:59,289 --> 00:08:01,500
<i>- What are we going to do?</i>
- No, no, no.

120
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:03,458
I just said "if."

121
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:07,016
I'm hanging up now.

122
00:08:15,208 --> 00:08:17,958
Big Bro, are you hungry?

123
00:08:17,958 --> 00:08:20,262
I'll go make you a late-night snack.

124
00:08:22,375 --> 00:08:26,229
Do you know what is most valuable?

125
00:08:28,791 --> 00:08:30,082
Big Bro.

126
00:08:30,082 --> 00:08:32,511
Information is the most valuable.

127
00:08:34,541 --> 00:08:36,708
I'm sorry, Big Bro.

128
00:08:36,708 --> 00:08:39,583
Did I cause trouble?

129
00:08:39,583 --> 00:08:41,916
What trouble could you possibly cause?

130
00:08:41,916 --> 00:08:44,458
I let you tag along because I wanted you to see

131
00:08:44,458 --> 00:08:46,781
how business is done.

132
00:08:51,250 --> 00:08:54,708
You sent that piece of news back home.

133
00:08:54,708 --> 00:08:56,791
What impact could that have?

134
00:08:56,791 --> 00:08:58,435
A few hundred bucks' worth of harvest?

135
00:08:59,583 --> 00:09:01,333
Do you have any idea how much money

136
00:09:01,333 --> 00:09:03,875
you could have made with that information?

137
00:09:03,875 --> 00:09:06,007
Don't you have any ambition?

138
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:10,375
If you're still going to be a useless loser,

139
00:09:10,375 --> 00:09:12,943
don't embarrass me tomorrow.

140
00:09:16,458 --> 00:09:17,458
No way.

141
00:09:17,458 --> 00:09:18,583
Can't you two be apart for even a second?

142
00:09:18,583 --> 00:09:19,833
Hey, hey, hey.

143
00:09:19,833 --> 00:09:22,041
Let's talk business.

144
00:09:22,041 --> 00:09:23,291
I've done the math.

145
00:09:23,291 --> 00:09:25,833
It'd be a huge loss to miss this market trend.

146
00:09:25,833 --> 00:09:28,541
I managed to squeeze
200,000 out of the old man.

147
00:09:28,541 --> 00:09:31,083
I got 200,000, too.

148
00:09:32,375 --> 00:09:35,832
So, how much more do you need?

149
00:09:35,832 --> 00:09:37,583
Actually, it's not that much.

150
00:09:37,583 --> 00:09:38,916
Just...

151
00:09:38,916 --> 00:09:40,419
Hold on a second.

152
00:09:43,166 --> 00:09:45,458
Fan Fan, Xiao Fan, hurry up!

153
00:09:45,458 --> 00:09:46,916
Something happened to your dad!

154
00:09:46,916 --> 00:09:48,541
- Xiao Fan.
- Yeah?

155
00:09:48,541 --> 00:09:50,514
It's your mom.

156
00:09:56,583 --> 00:09:58,291
Why is she calling my phone?

157
00:09:58,291 --> 00:09:59,625
<i>- Xiao Fan!</i>
- Mom.

158
00:09:59,625 --> 00:10:02,208
- What's wrong?
<i>- Something terrible happened!</i>

159
00:10:02,208 --> 00:10:04,416
Your dad panicked after hearing your news.

160
00:10:04,416 --> 00:10:05,916
<i>He borrowed the village chief's tricycle</i>

161
00:10:05,916 --> 00:10:07,333
<i>to go buy up wheat in town.</i>

162
00:10:07,333 --> 00:10:09,291
<i>He got hit by a car on the way!</i>

163
00:10:09,291 --> 00:10:10,375
Is Dad okay?

164
00:10:10,375 --> 00:10:11,833
<i>He's in the hospital now.</i>

165
00:10:11,833 --> 00:10:13,750
<i>The police say it was our fault.</i>

166
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:15,041
<i>Quick, send some money back.</i>

167
00:10:15,041 --> 00:10:16,375
<i>- Hurry!</i>
- Okay, got it.

168
00:10:16,375 --> 00:10:18,083
Mom, don't worry.

169
00:10:18,083 --> 00:10:19,959
I'll head back right away.

170
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,864
Big Bro.

171
00:10:29,958 --> 00:10:31,375
I have to go back to my hometown.

172
00:10:31,375 --> 00:10:32,948
Let's talk outside.

173
00:10:38,416 --> 00:10:40,583
Tell Manager Li to give me 5,000 in cash.

174
00:10:40,583 --> 00:10:41,750
Deduct it from this room's bill.

175
00:10:41,750 --> 00:10:43,062
Okay.

176
00:10:49,875 --> 00:10:51,333
I'm sorry, Big Bro.

177
00:10:51,333 --> 00:10:53,477
I'm still causing you trouble.

178
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,083
Go ahead.

179
00:11:01,083 --> 00:11:02,894
Give my regards to your mother.

180
00:11:07,125 --> 00:11:08,416
Thank you, Big Bro.

181
00:11:08,416 --> 00:11:10,300
Thank you.

182
00:11:13,208 --> 00:11:15,916
Big Bro, are you coming home tonight?

183
00:11:15,916 --> 00:11:17,867
I'll make you some soup.

184
00:11:19,207 --> 00:11:20,208
Don't bother.

185
00:11:20,208 --> 00:11:21,291
I haven't felt like having soup lately.

186
00:11:21,291 --> 00:11:23,157
How about I make you porridge instead?

187
00:11:34,583 --> 00:11:37,416
As they say, one's background
determines one's vision,

188
00:11:37,416 --> 00:11:39,208
and vision determines one's choices.

189
00:11:39,208 --> 00:11:41,333
That's enough, Master Zhuo.

190
00:11:41,333 --> 00:11:43,666
When Lv Qing comes back later
and sees you acting like this,

191
00:11:43,666 --> 00:11:45,450
do you think he'll be happy?

192
00:11:46,625 --> 00:11:49,375
Being gay isn't like a common cold.

193
00:11:49,375 --> 00:11:51,541
You can't just take a pill and be cured.

194
00:11:51,541 --> 00:11:54,500
Even if you drive Lu Xiao Fan away,

195
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:56,416
it won't change the facts.

196
00:11:56,416 --> 00:11:58,083
Red gates are for stone lions,

197
00:11:58,083 --> 00:12:00,125
and wooden gates are for bamboo horses.

198
00:12:00,125 --> 00:12:02,500
Lu Xiao Fan is just a peasant.

199
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:03,791
Do you really want Lv Qing

200
00:12:03,791 --> 00:12:06,250
to get bogged down in petty interests

201
00:12:06,250 --> 00:12:08,875
and commoner trivialities with him?

202
00:12:08,875 --> 00:12:12,416
Bei Lv Qing may like men,
but he deserves better.

203
00:12:12,416 --> 00:12:13,883
Fine, whatever.

204
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:20,250
<i>Hello, Fan Fan.</i>

205
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:21,500
<i>Are you doing okay over there?</i>

206
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:22,833
<i>Oh.</i>

207
00:12:22,833 --> 00:12:23,833
<i>Let me tell you.</i>

208
00:12:23,833 --> 00:12:26,375
<i>Lv Qing made a call
to the best hospital here.</i>

209
00:12:26,375 --> 00:12:28,083
<i>Your dad got admitted right away.</i>

210
00:12:28,083 --> 00:12:31,625
<i>He even arranged full checkups
for both of us.</i>

211
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:32,458
<i>Ah.</i>

212
00:12:32,458 --> 00:12:34,916
<i>Everything's great, we're doing fine.</i>

213
00:12:34,916 --> 00:12:36,833
<i>Anyway, take good care of yourself.</i>

214
00:12:36,833 --> 00:12:37,875
<i>Oh, and,</i>

215
00:12:37,875 --> 00:12:41,250
<i>be sure to thank Lv Qing for us.</i>

216
00:12:43,375 --> 00:12:44,667
<i>I heard</i>

217
00:12:44,667 --> 00:12:46,875
<i>Lv Xin's mom is coming back to the country.</i>

218
00:12:57,166 --> 00:12:58,928
All right.

219
00:12:58,928 --> 00:13:02,920
Congratulations to Lv Qing on his graduation.

220
00:13:08,166 --> 00:13:12,133
Lv Qing, do you really not plan
to continue your studies?

221
00:13:17,125 --> 00:13:18,666
I've already thought it through.

222
00:13:18,666 --> 00:13:22,200
I think it's better to start working early.

223
00:13:23,833 --> 00:13:26,625
The domestic market has just opened up.

224
00:13:26,625 --> 00:13:29,125
What's the use of more schooling?

225
00:13:29,125 --> 00:13:33,126
In the end, it's just
to secure some minor official post.

226
00:13:35,083 --> 00:13:39,125
Son, this is the start-up capital from me.

227
00:13:39,125 --> 00:13:40,833
Go out and make a name for yourself.

228
00:13:40,833 --> 00:13:43,541
Lv Qing has to report to
the Ministry of Foreign Affairs next week.

229
00:13:43,541 --> 00:13:46,333
Money from dubious sources is no good.

230
00:13:46,333 --> 00:13:48,833
Dubious sources?

231
00:13:48,833 --> 00:13:50,208
This is money from a mother to her son.

232
00:13:50,208 --> 00:13:53,416
How can you call it dubious?

233
00:13:53,416 --> 00:13:56,587
Or are you implying something, Mr. Bei?

234
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:06,250
Xiao Fan, Lv Qing has graduated.

235
00:14:06,250 --> 00:14:09,458
How about you stop living at the school dorms?

236
00:14:09,458 --> 00:14:11,416
Come and live at home.

237
00:14:11,416 --> 00:14:12,625
He hasn't been living
at school for a long time.

238
00:14:12,625 --> 00:14:13,984
Oh?

239
00:14:14,791 --> 00:14:17,981
Xiao Fan, you're not living on campus?

240
00:14:22,708 --> 00:14:25,333
I'm staying at Lv Qing's place now.

241
00:14:25,333 --> 00:14:29,107
I help him with the cleaning and the cooking.

242
00:14:33,166 --> 00:14:36,040
Xiao Fan was being bullied at school.

243
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:40,064
He's staying at my place
to lie low for a while.

244
00:14:52,125 --> 00:14:53,958
<i>The judiciary and the press agency</i>

245
00:14:53,958 --> 00:14:56,375
<i>held a joint press conference today.</i>

246
00:14:56,375 --> 00:14:57,666
<i>The CPPCC inspection team</i>

247
00:14:57,666 --> 00:14:59,291
<i>is inspecting the Yellow River Delta.</i>

248
00:14:59,291 --> 00:15:01,958
<i>Hanshan Power Plant's
first 300,000-kilowatt unit</i>

249
00:15:01,958 --> 00:15:03,125
<i>has begun generating power.</i>

250
00:15:03,125 --> 00:15:04,708
<i>The Prime Minister of India has withdrawn...</i>

251
00:15:04,708 --> 00:15:06,666
<i>Xiao Fan.</i>

252
00:15:06,666 --> 00:15:07,708
Big Bro.

253
00:15:07,708 --> 00:15:09,416
Will you be back for dinner tonight?

254
00:15:09,416 --> 00:15:10,875
<i>No.</i>

255
00:15:10,875 --> 00:15:12,666
You haven't been back for days.

256
00:15:12,666 --> 00:15:14,375
Do you need me to bring you anything?

257
00:15:14,375 --> 00:15:15,616
<i>I don't need anything.</i>

258
00:15:17,041 --> 00:15:18,666
<i>In the next couple of days,</i>

259
00:15:18,666 --> 00:15:21,083
<i>move your things back to the dorm.</i>

260
00:15:21,083 --> 00:15:23,048
<i>I'll be needing this place in the future.</i>

261
00:15:53,291 --> 00:15:54,625
There are only a few months until graduation.

262
00:15:54,625 --> 00:15:55,958
Why are you making such a fuss?

263
00:15:55,958 --> 00:15:58,025
Everyone else is out on internships.

264
00:15:59,957 --> 00:16:00,958
True.

265
00:16:00,958 --> 00:16:03,050
You don't need to bother with all that.

266
00:16:05,208 --> 00:16:07,416
All right. I've delivered all the invitations.

267
00:16:07,416 --> 00:16:09,625
Right, today is Lv Qing's birthday.

268
00:16:09,625 --> 00:16:11,792
You've already booked the private room?

269
00:16:13,625 --> 00:16:15,291
Sorry, I'm in the wrong room.

270
00:16:15,291 --> 00:16:16,833
Zi Yang.

271
00:16:16,833 --> 00:16:18,708
Oh! Xiao Fan!

272
00:16:18,708 --> 00:16:21,008
Why did you move back here?

273
00:16:21,791 --> 00:16:25,541
It's my brother's birthday?

274
00:16:25,541 --> 00:16:28,458
The presidential suite at Jinfan Hotel.

275
00:16:28,458 --> 00:16:29,958
What?

276
00:16:29,958 --> 00:16:31,925
Didn't your brother tell you?

277
00:16:34,083 --> 00:16:36,166
He's been very busy lately.

278
00:16:36,166 --> 00:16:38,083
I'm very busy, too.

279
00:16:38,083 --> 00:16:42,133
Busy keeping up with national affairs?

280
00:16:43,208 --> 00:16:46,541
Since I've graduated, I need to find a job.

281
00:16:46,541 --> 00:16:48,458
Why are you looking for a job yourself?

282
00:16:48,458 --> 00:16:50,083
Don't make the Bei family a laughingstock.

283
00:16:50,083 --> 00:16:51,958
Talk to Mr. Bei.

284
00:16:51,958 --> 00:16:55,333
Lv Qing and Wen Xi
have a lot to deal with every day now.

285
00:16:55,333 --> 00:16:56,791
Wen Xi.

286
00:16:56,791 --> 00:16:58,078
I'm off.

287
00:17:12,625 --> 00:17:14,625
Where did you buy this pen?

288
00:17:14,625 --> 00:17:16,166
This is a branded item.

289
00:17:16,166 --> 00:17:18,625
I bought it just for my advisor.

290
00:17:18,625 --> 00:17:20,000
How much was it?

291
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,806
120 yuan.

292
00:17:22,666 --> 00:17:25,581
That's half a year's internship pay for me.

293
00:17:52,833 --> 00:17:54,832
Are you happy that I'm here?

294
00:17:54,832 --> 00:17:57,207
- I am.
- How could Lv Qing be upset?

295
00:17:57,207 --> 00:17:59,166
- I'm very happy.
- Happy birthday.

296
00:17:59,166 --> 00:18:00,166
Thank you.

297
00:18:00,166 --> 00:18:04,470
You're still meeting up
every day behind our backs?

298
00:18:13,569 --> 00:18:15,054
Cheers!

299
00:18:17,083 --> 00:18:18,500
You two can't drink in secret.

300
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:19,708
Of course not.

301
00:18:19,708 --> 00:18:21,791
How can you call this "in secret"?

302
00:18:21,791 --> 00:18:23,125
Pour another glass. Fill it up!

303
00:18:23,125 --> 00:18:24,291
Cheers! Cheers! Cheers!

304
00:18:24,291 --> 00:18:25,523
Come on!

305
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:28,791
Li Wen Xi, where have you been?

306
00:18:28,791 --> 00:18:30,540
Why did it take you so long to return?

307
00:18:30,540 --> 00:18:31,625
It's been a long time since we've seen

308
00:18:31,625 --> 00:18:33,541
Young Master Bei this happy.

309
00:18:33,541 --> 00:18:35,750
Yeah. Look how joyful he is today.

310
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:38,333
- Take a penalty drink!
- Guys, let's have a drink. Bottoms up!

311
00:18:38,333 --> 00:18:39,375
Bottoms up!

312
00:18:39,375 --> 00:18:41,208
Bottoms up!

313
00:18:41,208 --> 00:18:42,375
Bottoms up!

314
00:18:42,375 --> 00:18:43,375
Bottoms up!

315
00:18:43,375 --> 00:18:44,833
I'm drinking?

316
00:18:44,833 --> 00:18:47,625
Young Master Bei, it's your birthday,
but all the drinks are coming my way.

317
00:18:47,625 --> 00:18:49,583
Bottoms up! Bottoms up!

318
00:18:49,583 --> 00:18:52,178
Bottoms up! Bottoms up!

319
00:18:54,416 --> 00:18:56,095
Let's do a cross-arm toast.

320
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:59,625
It's been a long time since we all gathered.

321
00:18:59,625 --> 00:19:01,041
Now that Li Wen Xi is back,

322
00:19:01,041 --> 00:19:02,375
he shouldn't be leaving again, right?

323
00:19:02,375 --> 00:19:04,000
Let him stay for a long time.

324
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,125
Come on, Master Bei.

325
00:19:05,125 --> 00:19:06,918
Then how long can I stay?

326
00:19:07,875 --> 00:19:10,000
Stay forever.

327
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:12,091
Are you serious?

328
00:19:13,875 --> 00:19:18,018
Then someone is going to be overjoyed, right?

329
00:19:19,708 --> 00:19:21,518
Not bad.

330
00:19:22,958 --> 00:19:24,875
Sir, are you going in?

331
00:19:24,875 --> 00:19:26,125
Hey.

332
00:19:26,125 --> 00:19:28,541
Isn't that Lu Xiao Fan?

333
00:19:28,541 --> 00:19:30,026
No.

334
00:19:55,375 --> 00:19:56,528
Big Bro.

335
00:19:58,541 --> 00:19:59,973
Big Bro.

336
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:12,558
Big Bro.

337
00:20:14,333 --> 00:20:16,015
Happy birthday.

338
00:20:19,375 --> 00:20:21,016
Happy birthday.

339
00:20:58,958 --> 00:21:00,382
Big Bro.

340
00:21:03,708 --> 00:21:07,853
Mr. Bei and Lv Xin are still upstairs.

341
00:21:15,833 --> 00:21:17,966
Are you scared?

342
00:21:18,916 --> 00:21:20,491
I...

343
00:21:28,583 --> 00:21:32,648
Then... keep your voice down.

344
00:21:49,541 --> 00:21:50,941
Big Bro.

345
00:21:56,916 --> 00:21:58,411
Big Bro.

346
00:22:03,294 --> 00:22:05,136
Big Bro.

347
00:22:09,041 --> 00:22:10,908
You've had too much to drink.

348
00:22:20,958 --> 00:22:22,400
Big Bro.

349
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,472
Fan Fan.

350
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,538
Big Bro.

351
00:22:45,375 --> 00:22:46,933
Big Bro.

352
00:25:15,458 --> 00:25:17,375
Since when did you like drinking coffee?
[Coffee]

353
00:25:17,375 --> 00:25:20,406
Your brother has always liked coffee.

354
00:25:21,583 --> 00:25:23,125
- Hello.
- You're here.

355
00:25:23,125 --> 00:25:24,506
Sit down.

356
00:25:27,666 --> 00:25:28,733
Why are you just standing there?

357
00:25:28,733 --> 00:25:30,027
Please, sit.

358
00:25:32,875 --> 00:25:33,917
I'm sorry.

359
00:25:33,917 --> 00:25:35,441
I booked this cafe.

360
00:25:35,441 --> 00:25:37,948
It's relatively quiet,
making it easier for us to talk.

361
00:25:39,250 --> 00:25:40,625
I just got back from Africa.

362
00:25:40,625 --> 00:25:42,125
I brought some fresh coffee beans.

363
00:25:42,125 --> 00:25:43,833
Everyone, please try some.

364
00:25:43,833 --> 00:25:46,414
Don't tell me you're addicted to coffee.

365
00:25:48,250 --> 00:25:51,666
There are only two things I'm addicted to.

366
00:25:51,666 --> 00:25:53,791
First is you,

367
00:25:53,791 --> 00:25:55,899
and second is coffee.

368
00:26:00,541 --> 00:26:02,748
You brought these back from Burundi, right?

369
00:26:02,748 --> 00:26:04,208
How did you guess?

370
00:26:04,208 --> 00:26:07,307
Indeed. It's fragrant and mellow.

371
00:26:20,416 --> 00:26:22,750
I'm sorry. Excuse me.

372
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:24,125
I'm sorry.

373
00:26:24,125 --> 00:26:25,958
I don't like sugar in my coffee,

374
00:26:25,958 --> 00:26:29,000
so I didn't add any for you all.

375
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:30,583
Let's get him a cappuccino instead.

376
00:26:30,583 --> 00:26:32,464
Isn't that a girl's drink?

377
00:26:35,333 --> 00:26:37,041
Just kidding.

378
00:26:37,041 --> 00:26:39,333
I often hear Lv Qing mention you,

379
00:26:39,333 --> 00:26:42,541
so I was quite curious about you.

380
00:26:42,541 --> 00:26:45,208
He said you aren't very fond of coffee.

381
00:26:45,208 --> 00:26:48,341
But I still insisted on inviting you over.

382
00:26:53,833 --> 00:26:54,959
Let's get to know each other.

383
00:26:54,959 --> 00:26:57,576
I'm Li Wen Xi. Nice to meet you.

384
00:27:02,666 --> 00:27:05,427
Hello. I'm Lu Xiao Fan.

385
00:27:08,208 --> 00:27:09,666
Hey, Lv Qing.

386
00:27:09,666 --> 00:27:11,787
Do you still play the piano?

387
00:27:12,666 --> 00:27:15,375
I haven't played since I came back.

388
00:27:15,375 --> 00:27:18,166
Why? You've been playing for so long.

389
00:27:18,166 --> 00:27:20,881
Actually, I never liked playing the piano.

390
00:27:25,875 --> 00:27:28,166
That's because you lacked a soulmate.

391
00:27:28,166 --> 00:27:29,961
Then I'm not leaving.

392
00:27:34,583 --> 00:27:35,500
Lv Qing.

393
00:27:35,500 --> 00:27:38,083
You still haven't thrown this away?

394
00:27:38,083 --> 00:27:40,500
Didn't you tell me not to take it off?

395
00:27:40,500 --> 00:27:42,531
I heard you've been on blind dates lately.

396
00:27:44,875 --> 00:27:46,208
Yes.

397
00:27:46,208 --> 00:27:48,366
But none of them were satisfactory.

398
00:27:49,333 --> 00:27:52,958
I don't like meddlers
or people who are too demanding.

399
00:27:52,958 --> 00:27:55,890
I'm afraid they'd be a nuisance to us.

400
00:28:02,500 --> 00:28:03,625
I've booked dinner.

401
00:28:03,625 --> 00:28:05,505
Xiao Fan, come with us.

402
00:28:10,541 --> 00:28:12,066
Okay.

403
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:30,446
You're here.

404
00:28:42,250 --> 00:28:44,500
Big Bro. Try this.

405
00:28:44,500 --> 00:28:46,474
It's the signature dish here.

406
00:29:04,208 --> 00:29:07,175
Big Bro. Try this.

407
00:29:09,666 --> 00:29:11,557
This is also delicious.

408
00:29:12,958 --> 00:29:14,981
Big Bro. Have some water.

409
00:29:20,916 --> 00:29:22,476
Here.

410
00:29:28,416 --> 00:29:29,997
This is also delicious.

411
00:29:32,875 --> 00:29:33,916
Xiao Fan.

412
00:29:33,916 --> 00:29:35,541
That's enough.

413
00:29:35,541 --> 00:29:37,517
Lv Qing has hands.

414
00:29:49,125 --> 00:29:50,492
Big Bro.

415
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:54,958
Are you coming back tonight?

416
00:29:54,958 --> 00:29:56,583
You have things to do tomorrow morning.

417
00:29:56,583 --> 00:29:59,133
I'll get up early to make you soup.

418
00:30:07,041 --> 00:30:08,476
Lv Qing.

419
00:30:09,333 --> 00:30:12,480
Xiao Fan... is just being kind.

420
00:30:26,291 --> 00:30:28,375
Xiao Fan.

421
00:30:28,375 --> 00:30:30,458
Xiao Fan.

422
00:30:30,458 --> 00:30:31,541
Get in the car.

423
00:30:31,541 --> 00:30:32,833
I'll wait for my brother.

424
00:30:32,833 --> 00:30:35,250
Your brother asked me to pick you up.

425
00:30:35,250 --> 00:30:36,532
Oh.

426
00:30:43,246 --> 00:30:44,918
What were you doing just now?

427
00:30:47,833 --> 00:30:50,333
I just wanted to try one more time.

428
00:30:50,333 --> 00:30:52,208
Hey, Lu Xiao Fan.

429
00:30:52,208 --> 00:30:54,000
What's going on in that head of yours?

430
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:55,541
Do you even know how to be a gay man?

431
00:30:55,541 --> 00:30:56,708
You know how it works, right?

432
00:30:56,708 --> 00:30:59,958
A gay man means being with one guy today,
and with another tomorrow.

433
00:30:59,958 --> 00:31:01,375
But look at you.

434
00:31:01,375 --> 00:31:04,599
One minute you're all mopey and whining,

435
00:31:04,599 --> 00:31:06,791
and the next, you're like
a dog guarding its food,

436
00:31:06,791 --> 00:31:07,791
clinging to Bei Lv Qing.

437
00:31:07,791 --> 00:31:10,500
Think about your relationship with him.

438
00:31:10,500 --> 00:31:12,625
And who is Li Wen Xi?

439
00:31:12,625 --> 00:31:15,791
He's Lv Qing's childhood sweetheart.

440
00:31:15,791 --> 00:31:18,527
He hasn't even given you the cold shoulder yet.

441
00:31:21,541 --> 00:31:22,791
Xiao Fan.

442
00:31:22,791 --> 00:31:24,537
We're friends.

443
00:31:24,537 --> 00:31:27,125
As your dear buddy, let me ask you one thing.

444
00:31:27,125 --> 00:31:30,446
Do you know what your most valuable trait is?

445
00:31:33,370 --> 00:31:35,887
It's that you're sensible.

446
00:31:35,887 --> 00:31:37,583
For a man like Lv Qing,

447
00:31:37,583 --> 00:31:39,500
the people pursuing him,

448
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:41,000
both men and women,

449
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:43,000
could form a line around the block.

450
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:46,012
Someone like you being by his side
is enough to make people envious.

451
00:32:10,125 --> 00:32:12,945
You're back. I specially made some soup today.

452
00:32:17,541 --> 00:32:21,541
Xiao Fan, I'm going to stay here
with Lv Qing for a while.

453
00:32:21,541 --> 00:32:25,723
So... I'm afraid you'll have to move out.

